賣人類大軍，各國軍隊一齊打擊喪屍呢種世界觀<br />\n隻驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係得幾丁友<br />\n如果行十步有堆軍隊，差佬打緊就話<br />\n呢家睇個款都係3分鐘收皮"},{"pid":"8a3bbf1ba5857240c80466968563318564de6065","tid":1116154,"uid":165499,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:36:27.000Z","msg":"我同3個fd玩得好開心<br />\n$200蚊我覺得好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a38e40140826d55ad4b5edae2ecb2682c7368747","tid":1116154,"uid":139465,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8a3bbf1ba5857240c80466968563318564de6065","tid":1116154,"uid":165499,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:36:27.000Z","msg":"我同3個fd玩得好開心<br />\n$200蚊我覺得好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"同fd玩 咩game都好玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3938be32b0f1a6ba4f2fb408dcaa71e550a9e69e","tid":1116154,"uid":185783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"隻game 暫時有3個缺點<br />\n射擊感低，殺死D屍冇咩血肉橫飛唔太刺激，唯一密密麻麻迫埋黎有壓迫感同掃底曬幾爽<br />\n爆炸燃燒彈亦麻麻地<br />\n<br />\n武器唔多，黎黎去去十款上下，職業技能有D廢同重複，大部份係加減傷，職業分化唔大冇咩強調職業特色冇專武<br />\n<br />\n故事章節太少，多數位置路線重複要死守，版圖人物模組唔同咁解<br />\n<br />\n不過好在都有人有俾報告<br />\n遊戲公司話會改善<br />\n所以依家算係先行版"},{"pid":"254b05db5067968a98d3060caf88220227c2c857","tid":1116154,"uid":205996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:34:55.000Z","msg":"好快悶"},{"pid":"220146b8739174405274ffc8e6e27b3f37ed8166","tid":1116154,"uid":107671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:59:52.000Z","msg":"所有野都重複又重複，仲要不停升lvl ，真係幾垃圾下"}]}